org.eclipse.gmt.modisco.workflow.mwe.workflow
Interface WorkflowParameter

Deprecated. 

@Deprecated
public interface WorkflowParameter

A representation of the model object 'Parameter'.

The following features are supported:

  • Name
  • Description
  • Connection
  • Required
  • Value Strategy
  • Type
  • Direction
